{{Infobox artwork | image_file = Marianne Stokes Melisande.jpg | image_size = 200px | title = Melisande | artist = [[Marianne Stokes]] | year = {{start date|1895}}–{{end date|1898}} | medium = [[tempera]] on canvas | city = [[Cologne]], [[Germany]] | museum = [[Wallraf-Richartz Museum]] }} '''''Melisande''''' is the name of a painting by the Austrian painter [[Marianne Stokes]]. It was painted with [[tempera]] on canvas, 1895-1898. It is currently at the [[Wallraf-Richartz Museum]] in [[Cologne]], [[Germany]].
