'''The Book Club Bible''' is a [[non-fiction]] [[anthology]] of [[book review|literary review]], with a foreword by [[Lionel Shriver]], whose novel ''[[We Need to Talk About Kevin]]'' has its own prominent entry.<ref>https://www.amazon.co.uk/Book-Club-Bible-Definitive-Member/dp/1843172690</ref> Aside from providing a synopsis for each book, the text also features background information on the author, suggested comparison volumes, a detailed historical context and starting points for group discussion. The intention of the anthology is to encourage book club members to seek out and discuss important contemporary or classical works.<ref>http://www.lovereading.co.uk/book/2251/The-Book-Club-Bible-by-.html</ref>
